INSTALLATION
    bsd can be easily compiled and installed. See file "INSTALL" for
    instructions. Please also have a look at the file "REQUIREMENTS" for
    information on the tools required to run, compile, and develop bsd.


DOCUMENTATION
    The directory "doc" contains a documentation of bsd. It can also be
    downloaded at <http://service-technology.org/files/bsd/bsd.pdf>. A
    tool paper describing a case study conducted with bsd can be found in
    the file "doc/toolpaper.pdf".
